            <p>Nintendo has announced two pastelly new Joy-Con 2 controller colours for <a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/platforms/switch-2">Switch 2</a>, and said they'll release next month.</p>
<p>The colours - officially Light Purple and Light Green (though I'd have called them Lavender and Turquoise) - are due to arrive 12th February, alongside Mario Tennis Fever on Switch 2. As far as I'm aware, these are the first new Joy-Con 2 colour variants offered for Switch 2. I'm sure they won't be the last.</p>
<div>

<p><span data-type="targeting">
